Final Rules Remember:

For Overriding:

✅ Parent-child relation required
✅ Same method name
✅ Same parameters
✅ Same or covariant return type
✅ Child access cannot be more restrictive
✅ final/private/static cannot be overridden
✅ Constructor cannot be overridden
✅ Runtime polymorphism

Overloading = same name, different input
Overriding = same method, different implementation



